p: Newly isolated DENV E gene sequences, as well as those available from the GenBank were aligned by using MUSCLE [ 16]. Phylogenetic trees were inferred using the Metropolis-coupled Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMCMC) method in MrBayes v3.1.2 [ 17], and the GTR+I+Ð“ 4 model was selected for MrBayes analyses.
